<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Sisters Elly and Becky Miles look for love side by side on the new season of The Bachelorette. </p>

<p>And the pair have revealed how they handled the prospect of falling for the same manduring filming of the reality dating show. </p>

<p>Speaking to New Idea magazine on Monday, Becky said the two sisters were determined not to let suitors come between them. </p>

<p>Duo: In an interview with New Idea on Monday, Bachelorette sisters Elly, 25, (left) and Becky Miles, 30, (right) revealed how they avoided falling for the same man on the reality show </p>

<p>'There were a few times where maybe both of us thought maybe someone was cute,' Becky revealed. </p>

<p>'But then one of us would be like: ''I want to pursue something,'' So when Elly would say that to me, I was like ''yeah, you get it, girl''.'  </p>

<p>Elly went on to say she has never shared an interest in the man her sister was dating, instead thinking of him more like a brother. </p>

<p>Competition: 'There were a few times where maybe both of us thought maybe someone was cute,' Becky revealed</p>

<p>Sisters first! Speaking of finding love, Becky said: 'One of us would be like: 'I want to pursue something,' So when Elly would say that to me, I was like 'yeah, you get it, girl'</p>

<p>'I'd never be like ''Oh, I'm going to see if I can get in myself'',' she added. 'It would never go that way.'   </p>

<p>The girls, however, did say they would be looking for someone who is down-to-earth, positive and respectful on the show.       </p>

<p>On Saturday, Elly and Becky revealed they have both found love on the show with Becky telling Stellar: 'We're very happy with our fellas.'</p>

<p>Bros: Elly went on to say she has never shared an interest in the man her sister was dating, instead thinking of him more like a brother</p>

<p>Double trouble: On Saturday, Elly and Becky revealed they have both found love on the show with Becky telling Stellar: 'We're very happy with our fellas' </p>

<p>While the double Bachelorette surprised many fans of the show, the sisters could not be happier taking that journey together.</p>

<p>In a trailer for the show, Becky tells her sister, 'I want to find love next to you. It will be magical,' as they prepared to meet their Bachelors. </p>

<p>Elly's appearance on The Bachelorette comes after she found herself being sent home by Matt Agnew on The Bachelor last year. </p>

<p>The brand new season of The Bachelorette will premiere on Wednesday, October 7 at 7:30pm on Channel 10.  </p>

